<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Pet Purchase Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #f7931e);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .pet-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 5px solid #ff6b35;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff6b35;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .paw-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="paw-icon">🐾</div>
            <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
            <p>Your new furry friend is coming home!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome {{petName}} to Your Family! 🎉</h2>
            
            <div class="pet-info">
                <h3>🐕 Pet Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{petName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> <span class="amount">${{amount}}</span></p>
                <p><strong>Purchase Date:</strong> {{purchaseDate}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>What's Next? 📋</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>🏠 Prepare your home for {{petName}}</li>
                <li>🛍️ Get essential supplies (food, toys, bed)</li>
                <li>👩‍⚕️ Schedule a vet checkup</li>
                <li>❤️ Show lots of love and patience</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>We're so excited for you and {{petName}}! If you have any questions, don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Thank you for choosing Pete's Pet Emporium!</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>🐾 Pete's Pet Emporium - Connecting Hearts with Paws</p>
            <p>© 2025 Pete's Pet Emporium. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>